---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services"
  description="Strategic growth advisory for growth-stage B2B SaaS companies at critical inflection points."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-8 text-balance" data-animate-hero>
        Growth strategy for inflection points
      </h1>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-gray-400" data-animate-hero-sub>
        I work with growth-stage B2B SaaS companies when the growth investment decision
        really matters—when you're trying to figure out whether to pour fuel on the fire
        or fix the engine first.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ideal Client -->
  <section class="section-sm border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-heading mb-6" data-animate>Is this you?</h2>
      <div class="prose-minimal">
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="0.1">
          You're a CEO, founder, or board member at a Series A-C B2B SaaS company. You've got
          product-market fit (or you're close), revenue is growing, but you're not sure if your
          growth is actually working or just correlating with a rising tide.
        </p>
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="0.15">
          You're asking questions like: Should we hire a CMO or keep the team lean? Is our
          pipeline problem a demand problem or a conversion problem? Why isn't our content
          driving leads? Are we ready to scale spend or will we just burn cash faster?
        </p>
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="0.2">
          Those are the questions I help answer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engagement Models -->
  <section class="section border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">How I Work</p>
      <h2 class="text-display mb-12" data-animate>Engagement Models</h2>

      <div class="space-y-16" data-animate-stagger="0.15">
        <!-- Advisory -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-small text-gray-400 mb-2">Advisory</p>
          <h3 class="text-heading mb-4">Strategic Counsel</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Ongoing access for CEOs and growth leaders who want a thinking partner.
            Monthly calls, async access, board prep, hiring decisions.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-small text-gray-400">
            <li>→ Monthly strategy sessions</li>
            <li>→ Async Slack/email access</li>
            <li>→ Board deck review</li>
            <li>→ Hiring and org design input</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Project -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-small text-gray-400 mb-2">Project</p>
          <h3 class="text-heading mb-4">Focused Engagements</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Defined-scope projects with clear deliverables. Demand gen audits, GTM strategy,
            positioning work, growth investment frameworks.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-small text-gray-400">
            <li>→ Growth investment audit</li>
            <li>→ GTM strategy development</li>
            <li>→ Positioning and messaging</li>
            <li>→ Channel strategy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Fractional -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-small text-gray-400 mb-2">Fractional</p>
          <h3 class="text-heading mb-4">Interim Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Part-time growth leadership while you search for a full-time hire or during
            a critical transition. Strategy and execution.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-small text-gray-400">
            <li>→ 2-3 days per week</li>
            <li>→ Team leadership</li>
            <li>→ Budget ownership</li>
            <li>→ Executive team participation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="section border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-heading mb-12" data-animate>How it starts</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12" data-animate-stagger="0.12">
        <div class="flex gap-8">
          <span class="text-display text-gray-700 shrink-0">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading mb-2">Conversation</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-gray-400">
              We talk for 30-45 minutes. I learn about your situation, you learn how I think.
              No pitch, just conversation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-8">
          <span class="text-display text-gray-700 shrink-0">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading mb-2">Diagnosis</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-gray-400">
              If there's a fit, I dig in. I'll review your data, talk to your team, and come
              back with an honest assessment of where you are.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-8">
          <span class="text-display text-gray-700 shrink-0">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-subheading mb-2">Proposal</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-gray-400">
              Based on what I find, I'll recommend an engagement model and scope. Clear
              deliverables, clear timeline, clear investment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-display mb-6" data-animate>Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-prose" data-animate data-animate-delay="0.1">
        If you're at an inflection point and want to think through your growth
        investment strategy, let's have a conversation.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:nick@strategnik.com" class="text-blue-bright hover:text-white transition-colors" data-animate data-animate-delay="0.2">
        Get in touch →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
